{"id":202276,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/12/北京密云将造“不说汉语”的英语城/","date":"2011-12-17T22:34:58Z","modified":"2011-12-17T22:34:58Z","title":"北京密云将造“不说汉语”的英语城","content":"<p>《新京报》报导，密云县县长王海臣宣布密云将建设“绿色国际休闲之都”，将在巨各庄镇蔡家洼村建一座占地千余亩的欧洲建筑风格的英语城，整个城分为16个城市街区，是个封闭式的城堡。开放后，进入英语城就像出国一样，弄一个“护照”然后盖章，进城之后不允许说汉语，说汉语会扣分。这将成为今后北京最大的欧洲风情小镇。<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/1b057088/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%AF%86%E4%BA%91%E5%B0%86%E9%80%A0%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%8D%E8%AF%B4%E6%B1%89%E8%AF%AD%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD%E5%9F%8E&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fsociety.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F12%2F16%2F0048240%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/12/260f6417emailthis2.gif.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%AF%86%E4%BA%91%E5%B0%86%E9%80%A0%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%8D%E8%AF%B4%E6%B1%89%E8%AF%AD%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD%E5%9F%8E&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fsociety.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F12%2F16%2F0048240%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/12/044291a1bookmark.gif.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/121585363240/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1b057088/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/121585363240/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1b057088/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=HszwhAP4soM:ivzAyQiZGXY:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=HszwhAP4soM:ivzAyQiZGXY:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" borde